data.description: Ask about the assumable mortgage & thousands in potential savings! Priced for interior updates! Those who know Oaklawn Park love it. Here are well-built homes with architectural variety on huge residential lots (this one is 100' wide, 125' deep!) with mature landscaping giving a unique sense of place that can not be replicated. Cloistered off of West Saint Mary Boulevard, these streets and neighborhood park cater to walking, running and bike riding. Passers-by won't realize how much space is here: huge rooms, including two living areas plus a pass-through office space, two dining areas, three full bathrooms, an oversized laundry room, and a corridor of closets which could be absorbed by the primary bedroom suite. HVAC & roof both replaced within a few years. Largely original interior.
